README:
# RF shimming in the cervical spinal cord at 7T

This is an MRI dataset acquired in the context of the project 'RF shimming in the cervical spinal cord at 7T'. 
Data were acquired at the Montreal Neurological Institute (Montreal, Canada) and at the Martinos Center for Biomedical Imaging (Boston, USA) on a Siemens Terra system using a 8Tx/20ch c-spine coil (https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/37439129/).

Repository of the project: https://github.com/shimming-toolbox/rf-shimming-7t
